# HQ cloud sync ignores.
#
# The sync engine is permissive by default: company data folders are meant to
# travel with the company's vault-backed workspace. Do not add
# `companies/*/data/` here unless a company has made an explicit local-only
# data decision.

# Company settings contain credentials and local tokens. These must never leave
# the machine, even when a sync run walks an entire company directory.
companies/*/settings/
companies/*/settings/**
